<template>
    <v-app-bar app color="primary" dark>
      <v-app-bar-nav-icon @click="toggleDrawer"></v-app-bar-nav-icon>
  
      <v-toolbar-title class="text-h6">Inventory Management</v-toolbar-title>
  
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
  
      <v-btn text @click="navigateTo('dashboard')">Dashboard</v-btn>
      <v-btn text @click="navigateTo('products')">Products</v-btn>
      <v-btn text @click="navigateTo('orders')">Orders</v-btn>
      <v-btn text @click="navigateTo('settings')">Settings</v-btn>
  
      <!-- Cart Icon -->
      <v-btn
        icon
        @click="navigateTo('cart')"
      >
        <v-icon>mdi-cart</v-icon>
      </v-btn>
    </v-app-bar>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    name: 'NavbarComponent',
    methods: {
      navigateTo(page) {
        this.$router.push({ name: page });
      },
      toggleDrawer() {
        // Optionally handle drawer toggling here if needed
      },
    },
  };
  </script>
  
  <style scoped>
  .v-app-bar {
    padding-left: 16px;
    padding-right: 16px;
  }
  </style>
